recommendations: Add tests for pagination and limit/offset parameters to ensure proper handling of large datasets.
Include explicit authorization tests to verify access control and permission restrictions.
Implement rate limiting tests to prevent abuse and verify system stability under load.
Add scenarios to verify caching headers and cache invalidation behavior.
